---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Turn Your ERP Data Into Revenue"
  description="Building materials distributors are sitting on millions in locked data. We turn it into real-time visibility that increases inventory turns, reduces stockouts, and drives margin."
>

  <!-- SECTION 1: Hero -->
  <section class="min-h-screen flex items-center bg-[#000510]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight max-w-4xl">
        Turn your ERP data into revenue.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-[#f5f4f0]/80 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
        Building materials distributors are sitting on millions in locked data. We turn it into real-time visibility that increases inventory turns, reduces stockouts, and drives margin — across purchasing, finance, sales, and operations.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
        <a href="#case-study" class="inline-block bg-[#16A34A] hover:bg-[#15803D] text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-center transition-colors shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(22,163,74,0.3)]">
          See How It Works
        </a>
        <a href="https://links.zenprocess.ai/widget/booking/rcoKJifJJA46bRI9fTEr" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block border border-white/20 hover:border-[#22C55E] text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-center transition-colors">
          Book a Discovery Call
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-12 text-sm text-[#6b5e75]">
        Built for companies running SAP &nbsp;|&nbsp; NetSuite &nbsp;|&nbsp; Microsoft Dynamics &nbsp;|&nbsp; Epicor &nbsp;|&nbsp; Sage &nbsp;|&nbsp; Infor &nbsp;|&nbsp; Spruce &nbsp;|&nbsp; BisTrack &nbsp;|&nbsp; DMSi &nbsp;|&nbsp; Acumatica &nbsp;|&nbsp; and any ERP with an API
      </p>
      <!-- Trust strip -->
      <div class="mt-8 flex items-center flex-wrap gap-4 text-sm text-[#978aa1]">
        <img src="/vinh-photo.jpg" alt="Vinh Truong" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-white/20 shrink-0" />
        <span class="text-white font-medium">Led by Vinh Truong</span>
        <span class="hidden sm:inline text-[#6b5e75]">|</span>
        <span>20+ yrs VP/CTO</span>
        <span class="hidden sm:inline text-[#6b5e75]">|</span>
        <span>$80M+ initiatives</span>
        <span class="hidden sm:inline text-[#6b5e75]">|</span>
        <span>Harvard · Stanford</span>
        <span class="hidden sm:inline text-[#6b5e75]">|</span>
        <span>M.S. Cybersecurity</span>
        <span class="hidden sm:inline text-[#6b5e75]">|</span>
        <span>CISSP · CEH</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 2: Problem Statement -->
  <section class="bg-[#000510] py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Sound familiar?</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#16A34A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M20.25 6.375c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125S3.75 8.653 3.75 6.375m16.5 0c0-2.278-3.694-4.125-8.25-4.125S3.75 4.097 3.75 6.375m16.5 0v11.25c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125V6.375m16.5 0v3.75c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125v-3.75m16.5 3.75v3.75c0 2.278-3.694 4.125-8.25 4.125s-8.25-1.847-8.25-4.125v-3.75" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Inventory turns are lower than they should be.</h3>
          <p class="text-[#f5f4f0]/80 leading-relaxed">
            Your team can't see what's moving across warehouses in real time. Purchasing, finance, and operations are all working off different spreadsheets with stale data.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#16A34A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 008.716-6.747M12 21a9.004 9.004 0 01-8.716-6.747M12 21c2.485 0 4.5-4.03 4.5-9S14.485 3 12 3m0 18c-2.485 0-4.5-4.03-4.5-9S9.515 3 12 3m0 0a8.997 8.997 0 017.843 4.582M12 3a8.997 8.997 0 00-7.843 4.582m15.686 0A11.953 11.953 0 0112 10.5c-2.998 0-5.74-1.1-7.843-2.918m15.686 0A8.959 8.959 0 0121 12c0 .778-.099 1.533-.284 2.253m0 0A17.919 17.919 0 0112 16.5a17.92 17.92 0 01-8.716-2.247m0 0A8.966 8.966 0 003 12c0-1.264.26-2.466.732-3.558" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Stockouts are costing you revenue.</h3>
          <p class="text-[#f5f4f0]/80 leading-relaxed">
            Your team finds out after the customer calls, not before. No proactive alerts, no early warning system — just reactive firefighting across multiple warehouses.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#16A34A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m-9.303 3.376c-.866 1.5.217 3.374 1.948 3.374h14.71c1.73 0 2.813-1.874 1.948-3.374L13.949 3.378c-.866-1.5-3.032-1.5-3.898 0L2.697 16.126zM12 15.75h.007v.008H12v-.008z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Every department runs on a different version of the truth.</h3>
          <p class="text-[#f5f4f0]/80 leading-relaxed">
            Purchasing pulls one spreadsheet, finance pulls another, sales has their own. Nobody has a single, real-time view of the business.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 3: Case Study Preview -->
  <section id="case-study" class="bg-[#000510] py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">What we built for a national building materials distributor</h2>
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">

        <div class="space-y-5">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#22C55E] shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
            </svg>
            <p class="text-[#f5f4f0]/80 text-lg">Multi-warehouse operation, SAP, 3,000+ SKUs</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#22C55E] shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
            </svg>
            <p class="text-[#f5f4f0]/80 text-lg">Real-time data refresh — replaced weekly Excel pulls</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#22C55E] shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
            </svg>
            <p class="text-[#f5f4f0]/80 text-lg">0.00% data variance on baseline validation</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#22C55E] shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
            </svg>
            <p class="text-[#f5f4f0]/80 text-lg">800+ daily inventory exceptions flagged automatically</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#22C55E] shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
            </svg>
            <p class="text-[#f5f4f0]/80 text-lg">Purchasing team uses the dashboard every morning</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[#22C55E] shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5" />
            </svg>
            <p class="text-[#f5f4f0]/80 text-lg">16-week engagement — started with a paid audit</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-8">
          <p class="text-sm text-[#978aa1] uppercase tracking-wider mb-6 font-semibold">Architecture</p>
          <div class="space-y-0">
            <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg px-5 py-4 text-center font-semibold">SAP</div>
            <div class="flex justify-center py-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#16A34A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 13.5L12 21m0 0l-7.5-7.5M12 21V3" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg px-5 py-4 text-center font-semibold">ETL/ELT</div>
            <div class="flex justify-center py-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#16A34A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 13.5L12 21m0 0l-7.5-7.5M12 21V3" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-lg px-5 py-4 text-center">
              <p class="font-semibold">Data Warehouse</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-[#978aa1] mt-1">Bronze / Silver / Gold</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-center py-2">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#16A34A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 13.5L12 21m0 0l-7.5-7.5M12 21V3" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-[#16A34A]/20 border border-[#16A34A]/30 rounded-lg px-5 py-4 text-center font-semibold text-[#22C55E]">Custom Dashboards</div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <a href="/case-study" class="inline-block bg-[#16A34A] hover:bg-[#15803D] text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(22,163,74,0.3)]">
          Read the Full Case Study
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 4: How It Works -->
  <section class="bg-[#000510] py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">How we work</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-8">
          <p class="text-5xl font-bold text-[#16A34A] mb-4">01</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-1">Paid AI Audit</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#978aa1] mb-4">2-4 weeks</p>
          <p class="text-[#f5f4f0]/80 leading-relaxed">
            We map your data flows, identify bottlenecks, and quantify the ROI of fixing them. You get a detailed report and clear recommendations — whether you hire us to build it or not.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-8">
          <p class="text-5xl font-bold text-[#16A34A] mb-4">02</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-1">Phased Implementation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#978aa1] mb-4">8-16 weeks</p>
          <p class="text-[#f5f4f0]/80 leading-relaxed">
            We build the data pipeline and dashboards in phases. Your team starts using real tools within weeks, not months. No disruption to daily operations. Built on top of your existing ERP.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-8">
          <p class="text-5xl font-bold text-[#16A34A] mb-4">03</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-1">Your Team Runs On It Daily</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#978aa1] mb-4">&nbsp;</p>
          <p class="text-[#f5f4f0]/80 leading-relaxed">
            We don't build demos. We build systems your purchasing and ops teams actually use. Training, SOPs, and handoff included. You own everything we build.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 5: Solutions Cards -->
  <section class="bg-[#000510] py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">What we build</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#16A34A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 013 19.875v-6.75zM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V8.625zM16.5 4.125c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25C20.496 3 21 3.504 21 4.125v15.75c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V4.125z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Real-Time Operational Dashboards</h3>
          <p class="text-[#f5f4f0]/80 leading-relaxed">
            Replace Excel reports with live dashboards your team opens every morning. Purchasing, inventory, finance — all from your existing ERP data. Real-time data refresh, not weekly.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#16A34A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7.5 21L3 16.5m0 0L7.5 12M3 16.5h13.5m0-13.5L21 7.5m0 0L16.5 12M21 7.5H7.5" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Modern Data Pipelines</h3>
          <p class="text-[#f5f4f0]/80 leading-relaxed">
            Your ERP data flows automatically into a cloud data warehouse. Bronze/Silver/Gold architecture ensures clean, validated data. No more manual exports, no more version conflicts.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-8">
          <div class="mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#16A34A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M14.857 17.082a23.848 23.848 0 005.454-1.31A8.967 8.967 0 0118 9.75v-.7V9A6 6 0 006 9v.75a8.967 8.967 0 01-2.312 6.022c1.733.64 3.56 1.085 5.455 1.31m5.714 0a24.255 24.255 0 01-5.714 0m5.714 0a3 3 0 11-5.714 0" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">Proactive Inventory Alerts</h3>
          <p class="text-[#f5f4f0]/80 leading-relaxed">
            Get notified before a stockout happens. Factor in overseas lead times (90-120 days), domestic suppliers (3-5 days), safety stock levels, and multi-warehouse transfers — automatically.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 6: ROI Calculator -->
  <section class="bg-[#000510] py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">What's your Excel habit costing you?</h2>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-8 md:p-10">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-10">

          <div>
            <label for="warehouses" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-[#f5f4f0]/80 mb-2">Number of warehouses</label>
            <select id="warehouses" class="w-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-[#16A34A]">
              <option value="1">1</option>
              <option value="2">2</option>
              <option value="3" selected>3</option>
              <option value="4">4</option>
              <option value="5">5+</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="skus" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-[#f5f4f0]/80 mb-2">SKUs managed</label>
            <select id="skus" class="w-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 text-white focus:outline-none focus:border-[#16A34A]">
              <option value="500">Under 500</option>
              <option value="2000" selected>500-2,000</option>
              <option value="5000">2,000-5,000</option>
              <option value="11000">5,000-11,000</option>
              <option value="11001">11,000+</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="hours" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-[#f5f4f0]/80 mb-2">
              Hours/week purchasing team in Excel: <span id="hours-value" class="text-[#22C55E] font-bold">15</span>
            </label>
            <input type="range" id="hours" min="5" max="40" value="15" class="w-full accent-[#16A34A] cursor-pointer" />
            <div class="flex justify-between text-xs text-[#6b5e75] mt-1">
              <span>5 hrs</span>
              <span>40 hrs</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <label for="stockouts" class="block text-sm font-semibold text-[#f5f4f0]/80 mb-2">
              Stockout incidents per month: <span id="stockouts-value" class="text-[#22C55E] font-bold">5</span>
            </label>
            <input type="range" id="stockouts" min="0" max="20" value="5" class="w-full accent-[#16A34A] cursor-pointer" />
            <div class="flex justify-between text-xs text-[#6b5e75] mt-1">
              <span>0</span>
              <span>20</span>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>

        <div class="border-t border-white/10 pt-8">
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center">
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-[#978aa1] mb-1">Annual cost of Excel dependency</p>
              <p id="excel-cost" class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">$35,100</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-[#978aa1] mb-1">Estimated stockout revenue loss</p>
              <p id="stockout-cost" class="text-3xl font-bold text-white">$150,000</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-[#978aa1] mb-1">Total annual cost of doing nothing</p>
              <p id="total-cost" class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#22C55E]">$185,100</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-8 text-center text-[#978aa1] max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        A $10K audit maps every data flow, quantifies every bottleneck, and delivers a detailed ROI report you can act on — with us or without us.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="https://links.zenprocess.ai/widget/booking/rcoKJifJJA46bRI9fTEr" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block bg-[#16A34A] hover:bg-[#15803D] text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(22,163,74,0.3)]">
          Book Your AI Audit
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 7: Credibility Strip -->
  <section class="bg-[#000510] py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center">
        <div>
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">20+ years</p>
          <p class="text-[#978aa1] mt-1">Enterprise IT & CTO leadership</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">$80M+</p>
          <p class="text-[#978aa1] mt-1">In technology initiatives delivered</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Production-grade</p>
          <p class="text-[#978aa1] mt-1">Data systems for building materials distribution</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Houston, TX</p>
          <p class="text-[#978aa1] mt-1">&nbsp;</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <a href="/about" class="text-[#22C55E] hover:text-[#16A34A] font-semibold transition-colors">
          About us &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 8: Final CTA -->
  <section class="bg-[#000510] py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
